    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="container about-grid">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.25rem;">Established in 2010, The Cherry Tree Cafe stands in a 400-year-old heritage estate in the heart of Hazratganj . Nestled in the Victorian charm of Habibullah Estate, we're known for our from-scratch recipes and hearty soul food. We bake our own bread and procure organic produce wherever possible .</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Whether you're savoring our signature blueberry cheesecake under the mango tree or enjoying our famous mac n' cheese indoors, we promise soul-satisfying food made with authentic recipes and the freshest produce .</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-highlight">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-tree"></i>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem;">☕ Since 2010</h3>
                <p>"The most loved brand of the city, practicing from-scratch recipes creating classics" </p>
                <hr style="margin: 20px 0; border-color: #dbb7a4;">
                <p><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> Open daily: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM </p>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i> ₹1,200 for two (approx.) </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

