                    <div class="menu-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-cake"></i><h4>Pancakes</h4><div class="menu-price">₹260</div><div class="menu-desc">4 fluffy pancakes with choice of toppings </div></div>
                    <div class="menu-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-bread-slice"></i><h4>Croissant French Toast</h4><div class="menu-price">₹240</div><div class="menu-desc">Served with butter and maple syrup </div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

